--- a/Documentation/admin-guide/mm/damon/usage.rst
+++ b/Documentation/admin-guide/mm/damon/usage.rst
@@ -66,7 +66,8 @@ comma (",").
     ‚îÇ :ref:`kdamonds <sysfs_kdamonds>`/nr_kdamonds
     ‚îÇ ‚îÇ :ref:`0 <sysfs_kdamond>`/state,pid,refresh_ms
     ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ :ref:`contexts <sysfs_contexts>`/nr_contexts
-    ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ :ref:`0 <sysfs_context>`/avail_operations,operations,addr_unit
+    ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ :ref:`0 <sysfs_context>`/avail_operations,operations,addr_unit,
+    ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ   pause
     ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ :ref:`monitoring_attrs <sysfs_monitoring_attrs>`/
     ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ ‚îÇ intervals/sample_us,aggr_us,update_us
